OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy at first today,
OL,6,Fbut some brighter spells will develop
OL,7,Fat times. A few spots of rain are
OL,8,Fpossible where the cloud thickens.
OL,9,FBreezy, but feeling pleasant in any
OL,10,Fsunny spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely dry and cloudy at
OL,13,Ffirst, but a spell of heavier rain
OL,14,Fwill arrive in the early hours.
OL,15,FStaying mild overnight under the
OL,16,Fblanket of cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
