OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FHeavy rain lingering in the
OL,6,Fmorning across northern parts of the
OL,7,Fregion, but gradually easing through
OL,8,Fthe day. Dry but largely cloudy in the
OL,9,Fsouth.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVery
OL,12,Fwarm over the Bank Holiday weekend
OL,13,Fwith plenty of sunshine and light
OL,14,Fwinds. However, some heavy, thundery
OL,15,Fshowers are possible on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
